{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/3-komik-ciayo-comics-pemenang-ciayo-short-story-challenge/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"3 Komik CIAYO Comics Pemenang CIAYO Short Story Challenge","content":"\n<p>Di tahun 2017 lalu, CIAYO Short Story Challenge diadakan dan berhasil menjaring lebih dari 100 submisi. Para writer berkompetisi menciptakan cerita pendek paling keren untuk mendapatkan hadiah tablet dan uang tunai, plus adaptasi komiknya di CIAYO Comics!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"19338\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/dukung-short-story-kesukaanmu/attachment/ciayo-short-story-isi-608-x-320-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/CIAYO-SHORT-STORY-isi-608-x-320-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"CIAYO SHORT STORY isi 608 x 320 2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/CIAYO-SHORT-STORY-isi-608-x-320-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/CIAYO-SHORT-STORY-isi-608-x-320-2.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/CIAYO-SHORT-STORY-isi-608-x-320-2.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Short Story Challenge. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-19338\"/><figcaption>CIAYO Short Story Challenge. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Setelah empat bulan proses submisi dan kurasi, akhirnya terkumpul 10 besar yang mendapatkan hadiah. Namun, dari mereka ada lagi <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/pengumuman-pemenang-ciayo-short-story-challenge/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">tiga pemenang</a> yang berhasil menjadikan cerita pendeknya menjadi komik betulan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Penasaran cerita pendek apa aja yang dijadikan komik di\nCIAYO Comics? Simak daftarnya berikut ini!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Cerita Pendek CIAYO Short Story Challenge Yang Dijadikan Komik</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3>Juara 3: Eversphere</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53942\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/3-komik-ciayo-comics-pemenang-ciayo-short-story-challenge/attachment/01-short-story-comic-winner/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-short-story-comic-winner.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-short-story-comic-winner\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-short-story-comic-winner-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-short-story-comic-winner.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-short-story-comic-winner.jpg\" alt=\"Eversphere. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53942\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-short-story-comic-winner.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-short-story-comic-winner-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Eversphere. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Eversphere adalah game VRMMO yang kini tengah digandrungi\nbanyak orang. Separuh besar pemainnya berasal dari Indonesia, dimana terdapat\nbanyak sekali pemain kuat dengan level tinggi. Salah satunya adalah Chase\nJuniar yang merupakan pemain terkuat kedua di seluruh game. Kehebatan Chase\nternyata jadi incaran pemain lain, dimana seorang hacker dan pemain Eversphere\nterkuat bernama Naciens berniat mengajak Chase menguasai seisi game. Ia bahkan\ntak ragu menculik Kayla, teman Chase, agar ia mau menurut. Bagaimana aksi Chase\nmenyelamatkan temannya dan menggagalkan rencana Naciens?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kisah karya Andry Chang ini menampilkan banyak sekali adegan\naksi dari awal sampai akhir. Nuansa ala komik shonen jadi fokus utama, dimana\nkekuatan persahabatan dan rasa percaya diri menjadi kepingan puzzle yang\nmelengkapi kehebatan Chase.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu bisa baca short story Eversphere <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/ciayostories/eversphere/\" target=\"_blank\">di sini</a>, dan komiknya <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/eversphere\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">di sini</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/kiat-kiat-dari-andry-chang-juara-3-ciayo-short-story-challenge/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Kiat-kiat Dari Andry Chang, Juara 3 CIAYO Short Story Challenge</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Juara 2: One Way Thread</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53943\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/3-komik-ciayo-comics-pemenang-ciayo-short-story-challenge/attachment/02-short-story-comic-winner/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-short-story-comic-winner.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-short-story-comic-winner\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-short-story-comic-winner-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-short-story-comic-winner.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-short-story-comic-winner.jpg\" alt=\"One Way Thread. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53943\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-short-story-comic-winner.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-short-story-comic-winner-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>One Way Thread. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Meskipun belum menjadi dokter dan tengah kuliah kedokteran,\nAndre sudah dijuluki sebagai dokter cinta. Pasalnya, Andre bisa melihat benang\nmerah yang saling menghubungkan pasangan sejati. Ironisnya, Andre tidak bisa\nmelihat benang miliknya sendiri. Semua berubah ketika Andre yang galau bertemu\ndengan Arisa yang punya kemampuan membaca aura seseorang.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keunikan One Way Thread karya Kuroi Sato ini adalah premis\nunik yang dipadukan dengan dialog dan interaksi menarik antara karakternya.\nMengangkat tema romance, komik ini sangat relatable bagi kamu yang tengah\nmencari soulmate sejati.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu bisa baca short story One Way Thread <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/ciayostories/one-way-thread/\" target=\"_blank\">di sini</a>, dan komiknya <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/one-way-thread\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">di sini</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Juara 1: Afterlife</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53944\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/3-komik-ciayo-comics-pemenang-ciayo-short-story-challenge/attachment/03-short-story-comic-winner/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-short-story-comic-winner.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-short-story-comic-winner\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-short-story-comic-winner-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-short-story-comic-winner.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-short-story-comic-winner.jpg\" alt=\"Afterlife. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53944\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-short-story-comic-winner.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-short-story-comic-winner-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Afterlife. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ria dan Roland adalah sepasang kekasih yang berkuliah di\nStanford. Ria tengah mengerjakan disertasi tentang mati otak, dan Roland sebagai\npacarnya mendukung sepenuh hati. Namun seiring waktu berjalan, setelah\nkelulusan mereka berdua dan pertunangan mereka, ternyata tujuan utama riset Ria\nadalah untuk mencari kehidupan setelah mati. Akankah mereka melanjutkan\neksperimen untuk mencurangi kematian tersebut?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pemenang CIAYO Short Story Challenge ini memiliki cerita\nyang sangat padat. Jeremiah Pranajaya selaku penulis menggabungkan genre horor,\ndrama, sains fiksi, hingga horor thriller dalam sebuah cerita emosional dan\nmenengangkan.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu bisa baca short story <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/afterlife\" target=\"_blank\">Afterlife</a> di sini, dan komiknya <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/ciayostories/afterlife/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">di sini</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"25079\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/pose-bareng-hadiah-ciayo-short-story-challenge/attachment/resize3-7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/resize3-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Jeremiah Pranajaya (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Jeremiah Pranajaya (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/resize3-5.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/resize3-5.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/resize3-5.jpg\" alt=\"Jeremiah Pranajaya, author Afterlife pemenang CIAYO Short Story Challenge. (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures) \" class=\"wp-image-25079\"/><figcaption>Jeremiah Pranajaya, author Afterlife pemenang CIAYO Short Story Challenge. (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures) </figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Itu dia tiga cerita pendek CIAYO Short Stories Challenge yang menjadi juara dan dikomikkan. Komik mana yang jadi favoritmu? Atau justru cerita favorit kamu nggak menjadi pemenangnya? Yuk cerita-cerita di kolom komentar!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"abb6f5d2-ab43-5c0c-b079-f90b6c3aaf2e"}}}